A \cap B \subseteq C \wedge A^c \cap B \subseteq C \Rightarrow B \subseteq C
 \begin{array}{rcl}  B & = & (A \cap B) \cup (A^c \cap B) \\   & = & (A \cap B) \cup B , \text{definition of intersection} \\   & = & B \, \square \end{array} 
